all rivalry|rivalry]]\n| tv = ESPN3\n| score         = '''EMU''' 17\u20137\n| attend        = 13,468\n}}\n{{CFB Conference Schedule End|timezone=[[Eastern Time Zone|Eastern Time]]}}\n\n'''Players of the Week'''<ref>[https://getsomemaction.com/news/2018/11/5/mac-announces-week-ten-football-players-of-the-week.aspx ANNOUNCES WEEK TEN FOOTBALL PLAYERS OF THE WEEK]. http://getsomemaction.com (2018-11-5). Retrieved on 2018-11-8.</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"display: inline-table;\"\n|-\n|+ East Division\n! colspan=\"2\" | Offensive\n! colspan=\"2\" | Defensive\n! colspan=\"2\" | Special teams\n|- align=\"center\"\n|-\n! Player\n! Team\n! Player\n! Team\n! Player\n! Team\n|-\n|Tyree Jackson\n|Buffalo\n|Dalton Hicks\n|Kent State\n|Alvin Floyd\n|Ohio\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"display: inline-table;\"\n|-\n|+ West Division\n! colspan=\"2\" | Offensive\n! colspan=\"2\" | Defensive\n! colspan=\"2\" | Special teams\n|- align=\"center\"\n|-\n! Player\n! Team\n! Player\n! Team\n! Player\n! Team\n|-\n|Tre Harbison\n|Northern Illinois\n|Jalen McKie\n|Northern Illinois\n|Jameson Vest\n|Toledo\n|}\n\n====Week Eleven====\n{{CFB Conference Schedule Start}}\n{{CFB Conference Schedule Entry\n| w/l           = \n| date          = {{tooltip|November 6|Tuesday}}\n| time          = 7:30 p.m.\n| visiting_team = '''Kent State'''\n| home_team     = '''Buffalo'''\n| site_stadium = UB Stadium\n| site_cityst = Buffalo, NY\n| tv = ESPNU\n| score         = '''UB''' 48\u201314\n| attend        = 15,078\n}}\n{{CFB Conference Schedule Entry\n| w/l           = \n| date          = {{tooltip|November 7|Wednesday}}\n| time          = 7:00 p.m.\n| visiting_team = '''Ohio'''\n| home_team     = '''Miami (OH)''' \n| site_stadium = Yager Stadium\n| site_cityst = Oxford, OH\n| gamename = [[Battle of the Bricks]]\n| tv = ESPNU\n| score         = '''MIOH''' 30\u201328\n| attend        = 15,975\n}}\n{{CFB Conference Schedule Entry\n| w/l           = \n| date          = {{tooltip|November 7|Wednes