do-2020-sanders-biden-and-warren-lead-democratic-field-democrats-look-to-gain-senate-seat/ Emerson College]\n| August 16\u201319, 2019\n| 1,000\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.0%\n| 45%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}| '''55%'''\n| \u2013\n|}\n\n;with Donald Trump and Kamala Harris\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Donald<br>Trump (R)\n! Kamala<br>Harris (D)\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [http://emersonpolling.com/2019/08/20/colorado-2020-sanders-biden-and-warren-lead-democratic-field-democrats-look-to-gain-senate-seat/ Emerson College]\n| August 16\u201319, 2019\n| 1,000\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.0%\n| 48%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}| '''51%'''\n| \u2013\n|}\n\n;Donald Trump vs. Amy Klobuchar\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Donald<br>Trump (R)\n! Amy<br>Klobuchar (D)\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://climatenexus.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Colorado-Poll-Climate-Change-Toplines.pdf Climate Nexus]\n| Feb 11\u201315, 2020\n| 485 (RV)\n| \u00b1&nbsp;4.5%\n| '''43%'''\n| '''43%'''\n| 14%\n|}\n\n;Donald Trump vs. Bernie Sanders\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Donald<br>Trump (R)\n! Bernie<br>Sanders (D)\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://climatenexus.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Colorado-Poll-Climate-Change-Toplines.pdf Climate Nexus]\n| Feb 11\u201315, 2020\n| 485 (RV)\n| \u00b1&nbsp;4.5%\n| 43%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}| '''48%'''\n| 9%\n|-\n| style=\"text-a